com.esri.mo2.file.shp
Interface ShapeZ

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, Shape, ShapeM
All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiPointZShp, PointZShp
public interface ShapeZ
extends ShapeM

This class declares the methods that are common to all non-multipart shapes with Z values. The starting index for points is 0.
